OL,5, The parents of a boy killed in a       
OL,6, collision at an indoor ski slope have  
OL,7, spoken of how they held him as he died.
OL,9,FTwelve-year-old Louis Watkiss, from    
OL,10,FSutton Coldfield, died at the Tamworth 
OL,11,FSnowDome in Staffordshire in September.
OL,13,FParents Chris and Natalie Watkiss were 
OL,14,Fat home when they got a call to say    
OL,15,FLouis had been hurt during a           
OL,16,Ftobogganing party with friends.        
OL,18,FThe couple are now calling for a change
OL,19,Fin the law to make helmets compulsory  
OL,20,Fduring similar activities.             
